data.text: So much L.O.V.E. to @JonCaramanica, @mehpatrol, @JoeCoscarelli for this piece of music history. It's like a coming out for one of my guiltiest pleasures. #AshleeSimpson #JessicaSimpson
"Was Ashlee Simpson Underappreciated? Discuss" is the first part, which centres on her music in the context of the early 2000s: https://t.co/1399ubP73f
